snippet.title: [STEAM] 100% Achievement Gameplay: Choco Rabbit Revenge
snippet.description:
Complete playthrough of Choco Rabbit Revenge, a generic 2D platformer. Achievements are just for scoring 10K, and beating the game. Third one of these asset flips I've played.



Like and subscribe for more content~
Let me know in the comments what you thought about the game or your personal experience with it! Also, feel free to leave any suggestions on fun games or stuff you'd like to see me achievement hunt on Steam.
